hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好型咁話 大過 小過你鐘意 記就記啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起都覺得 青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然好7<br />\n喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fa95b0df555fa2213d3a9eb6449130f6a40c52","tid":435060,"uid":38651,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"唔係自己選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但記得某年有一隊學生會 基本上坐定粒六個隻 點知就係咁而串串貢得罪好多人 又唔準備好啲 結果出現成間學校歷史上第一次得一隊而不信任票多過信任票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好記得點票個陣佢地個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9176ae4a2253a576880fbd35bceaeeac8f464101","tid":435060,"uid":33422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:10:36.000Z","msg":"六年以嚟無論學業定課外活動都無上過台攞獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後一年陸運會先去跑社際比賽，跑頭三點知唔頒獎俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個中學最威就係係大學返嚟攞dse獎學金<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 六年唯一榜上有名就係第七年先實現"},{"pid":"afbedcc772f3ee1d26a728b0993df173f8ceabeb","tid":435060,"uid":150983,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"追住個肥仔嚟打，打到佢早退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca168093004f4271499e49e53721f0f2bc7d9051","tid":435060,"uid":152058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:26:51.000Z"